        <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <h2 class="mb-3 text-primary">Our Story & Commitment</h2>
                <p>
                    Our mission is simple yet profound: to deliver high?quality, patient?centered healthcare with unwavering integrity and continuous innovation. We strive to be a trusted partner in your health journey, focusing on personalized care that respects your unique needs and values.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    Every decision we make—from advanced treatments to warm, human interactions—is rooted in this mission. True healing embraces medical excellence, empathy, and understanding.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/doctor-team.jpg" alt="Doctors Team" class="img-fluid shadow-sm rounded hover-lift" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/600x400?text=Doctors+Team';">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Care Pillars -->
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Our Care Pillars</h3>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="feature-card glass-card h-100 p-3 hover-3d">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-heart-pulse text-danger fs-2 me-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="mb-1">Patient?First</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Personalized treatment plans focused on your goals and comfort.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="feature-card glass-card h-100 p-3 hover-3d">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-cpu text-primary fs-2 me-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="mb-1">Technology?Enabled</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Modern diagnostics and digital records for efficient, safe care.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="feature-card glass-card h-100 p-3 hover-3d">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-success fs-2 me-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="mb-1">Quality & Safety</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Strict protocols and continuous improvement at every step.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="feature-card glass-card h-100 p-3 hover-3d">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock-history text-warning fs-2 me-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="mb-1">Timely Access</h5>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Convenient appointments and coordinated care across teams.</p>
