        <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-7 order-lg-2">
                <h2 class="mb-3 text-primary">Our Vision</h2>
                <p>
                    We envision HMS as a leading healthcare institution, globally recognized for excellence in medical care, research, and education. We continuously embrace new technologies to push the boundaries of healthcare and foster a healthier community.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-0">Beyond treating illness, we promote wellness, prevent disease, and empower individuals through education.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5 order-lg-1 text-center">
                <img src="~/images/modern-interior.jpg" alt="Modern Hospital Interior" class="img-fluid shadow-sm rounded hover-lift" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/600x400?text=Hospital+Interior';">
